Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗留下来的人

Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到对方竟然自己送上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将以这一击 回归那怀念的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远距离攻击魔法 准备术式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备术式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 随同部队传来联络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里曼机关的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以第一先遣队的指挥官为人质
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求与司令官对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他有话等结束再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一先遣队的指挥权移交给副官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续作战行动 就这样回复过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等这天等得好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能被些琐碎杂事打扰到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一击 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一击 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开防御魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显现吧 拦截者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Interceptor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动攻击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多少时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有看门狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽特拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面似乎就算放弃你也要继续作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身守护君主部下领民才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玷污了我作为先锋的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷下方中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何索厄拉的攻击能击穿我方防御魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是该我们占优的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:03:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来只可能是装载的魔法思念料的差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续 不要减缓攻击力度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念料的纯度可是不同的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻对面阵脚大乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐军 对我们来说不过是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往首都的碍脚石而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有魔法防壁在 应该不至于立即被击坠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 你情况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神支配的术式应该已经解除了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我该道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我们也是因时势才如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这句话我轻松许多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再相遇 可以毫不顾忌地杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大致说明下现在情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我基本都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有意识 也有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗不住想受敌人支配的强烈欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此不舒服的感受我还是第一次经历
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫葛拉特的魔法师 我必须要好好谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 比起这事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下更重要的是兄长和嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁 肯定没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉也…芙蕾多妮卡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体 回收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归 和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 加瓦尔尼公爵家的人们已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 里加尔图自身言明已把所有人杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芙蕾多妮卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脱皮了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是输了一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我汲取教训 把身体改为了双重构造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这样保温性也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 托鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长往最顶层去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡也在最上面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尽快与兄长他们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你吗 顺便带上她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这荒唐的生物到底是怎么回事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央部中弹 魔法机关受损
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法维持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胆怯 开炮 开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 李奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击魔法失去准头了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎发射口中弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这样 即使到了首都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法发动魔法攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里加尔图大人 葛拉特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么办法? 告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这要塞本身当作炮弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对维马克王宫发起突击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并发动魔法自爆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有索厄拉的魔法力在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应能将整个卡多威尔夷为平地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自身成为新战争的导火索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在历史上留下痕迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若维马克王国遭遇实际上的灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个大陆都会陷入混乱的漩涡中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是蕾拉 你总会为我们指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为里加尔图大人和葛拉特大人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉献上一切就是我的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 也是我的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合军的航天要塞已处于毁灭状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着首都卡多威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 别想全身而退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然回归王国无望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要拉你们一起上路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将剩余的功率全都使出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 在就回话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁断皇帝阿图尔·贾兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用双手创造了历史的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天 我也能与他比肩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾兹皇帝的愿望 也会由我的双手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了我的话 还有逃跑的力气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么想要这遗体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 原来入侵者是你们呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次见到蕾拉以外的「嘉依卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里加尔图·加瓦尔尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你父亲的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待 竟有幸亲手切割「嘉依卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要塞将突入首都卡多威尔自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体也好 「嘉依卡」也好 都会化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 放弃 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁 会来 必定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为钢也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 嘉依卡刚才还在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是司令室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群家伙到底有多少只啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有杀过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着慢着 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得报刚才的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有点累?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的内脏是什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 输了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不是战斗 你只是用刀在刺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这就是生命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只要自己死一次 就能明白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁 伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 赶紧回收遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然撞了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是纠缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎负责操纵的魔法师被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的达成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只剩如何逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍旧寻求遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的答覆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你接受自己工具的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就作为工具腐朽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salimic binnu allay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显现吧 强击者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Slugger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Floater
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托鲁 救助成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说多少次 乱破师只是雇主的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人为工具而冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可谓本末倒置…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 托鲁 工具 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工具 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索厄拉 在下沉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管你帮了我们那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 里加尔图大人和葛拉特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意陪我复仇至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能成为贾兹皇帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的活法 我的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我自己选的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定让基烈特大人担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然空手而归…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是该活捉嘉依卡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇 芷依塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我跟着还…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在骗我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇 队长他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人骗人 你们骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信 不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…你们骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 薇薇 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被创造的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么「收集遗体」本身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是某人为达到目的而设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那你自己想怎么办啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体 收集 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 其他没有 什么都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体 收集 想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托鲁 和阿卡莉 和芙蕾多妮卡 一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决意不变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助 可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还讲这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选你为主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是假货还是被人利用 这都无关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与兄长一心同体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会追随到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干脆和我签契约算了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若今后还要这样乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆和我签订契约 成为龙骑士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用一一疗伤了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说笑呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要出发还是趁早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定基烈特小队会追来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 走吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新英雄 喜好葡萄酒 美魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 魔法技术 本领了得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 托鲁 阿卡莉 苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 败退?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 收集遗体的皇女

